{"tid":1026492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「幣少爺」遭市民入稟　追討12.5萬元挖礦機貨款及存倉費","createTime":"2019-02-18T07:13:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T07:21:24.000Z","uid":75969,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0933b95996dd16996d9f6f75185acea9d7e21c37","tid":1026492,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T07:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190218/s00001/f70f49639a6c2933cd10da6f0d9c91df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190218%2Fs00001%2Ff70f49639a6c2933cd10da6f0d9c91df.jpg&h=be21f4d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n涉嫌策劃深水埗高空撒錢的「幣少爺」黃鉦傑，上周五遭市民入稟區域法院，追討12.5萬元購買「挖礦機」貨款及相關存倉費用。<br />\n<br />\n入稟狀顯示，原告關浩樑向被告黃鉦傑及「幣少集團有限公司」，追討5部「IPFS-FILECOIN Mining Machines」虛礙貨幣挖礦機的貨款，共12.5萬元，另加從本年1月19日至今的有關存倉費用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190218/s00001/1550468363244/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190218%2Fs00001%2F1550468363244%2F&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgEtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=65d90d6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190218%2Fs00001%2F1550468363244%2F&h=0334a0ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190218/s00001/1550468363244/</a>"},{"pid":"c43e3bd57b450455442a1aad0b4fe8235c172a35","tid":1026492,"uid":228963,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T07:14:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d0c26ced889b7331a5c22fd0ed6729b4a82edcc","tid":1026492,"uid":45672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T07:14:56.000Z","msg":"智力無下限"},{"pid":"64499d7746fc99e99f28769e1a134fe187ae8abd","tid":1026492,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T07:21:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSUw5X